{"tid":56691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日打左陣數碼暴龍世界 我看透左人生","createTime":"2016-12-27T12:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T12:18:21.000Z","uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02fbb847076ae7f3d2f8813784a780556c1fb111","tid":56691,"uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"頭先開返隻陳年數碼暴龍出來打<br />\n<br />\n諗住用極限既方式練一隻超班既出黎<br />\n<br />\n有隻野出世開始一路都冇做過其他事<br />\n<br />\n淨係訓練<br />\n<br />\n開頭一切都好順利<br />\n<br />\n隻野仲因為訓練成績好 令到我自己都升咗grade<br />\n<br />\n之後唔知點解跟足晒條件就係升唔到完全體<br />\n<br />\n佢就咁死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己好仆街 好似d怪獸家長咁<br />\n<br />\n我喊撚咗出黎 我睇到我自己<br />\n<br />\n讀咁多書有撚用<br />\n<br />\n人真系要活在當下 唔好因為將來而忘記左現在<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}